      <title>伊利诺伊州禁止公司强迫工人听取反工会言论</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/07/30/nx-s1-5040451/captive-audience-anti-union-religious-meetings-afl-cio</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊利诺伊州是第八个通过法律的州，该法律禁止雇主举行强制性的宗教、政治或反工会会议，此举旨在帮助试图成立工会的工人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/07/30/nx-s1-5040451/captive-audience-anti-union-religious-meetings-afl-cio</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 16:41:51 GMT</pubDate>
